#

Pineapple Ginger Juice

10 min
$5
90 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Dietary Tags:

VeganGluten-FreeDairy-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Beverage

Tags:

JuiceRefreshingHealthy

Description

A refreshing, zesty juice that combines the sweetness of pineapple with the spicy kick of ginger.

Ingredients

  • fresh pineapple: 1 medium
  • fresh ginger root: 1 inch
  • water: 2 cups
  • honey (optional): 1-2 tablespoons
  • ice cubes: as needed
